            Port of Entry
          </span>
          
            
              
                
                
              
            
          
        </button>
      </h4>
      
        
          <p class="">Port of Entry refers to a location where an individual may enter Canada (typically through airports, land borders, or marine crossings). </p><p class=""> </p><p class=""> </p><p class=""> </p><p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class=""></p>
        
      

      
        
      

